name: Add new Timeular time entries to Google Sheets spreadsheet
description: Every time there is a new time entry in Timeular, Make will automatically add a new row to specified Google Sheets spreadsheet. The template uses this [example spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1_xpsOjBjx3C-RIkB5qPzasVWvrKOuT6NbFMbQrP2NlE/edit?usp=sharing).
